    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's helpful. I just want to make sure I'm not being too soft. It really feels like their mistakes are almost like they're actively pulling the team down or causing mischief, even if it's not intentional. Is there a way to convey that their presence is actually causing a bit of a mess for the rest of the office without using \"unprofessional\" language?",
